      About this item

      • Individual Control of 2 IN 1 Outlets: 2 AC outlets are working and controlled independently. 15A/1800W Max for each. Waterproof cover is attached to protect it from dirt when not in use. Group your Ghome Smart light bulbs, plugs and switches for seamless control. Ideal for controlling all your devices simultaneously with a single tap.
      • IP64 Waterproof: GHome Smart outdoor smart plugs are up to IP64 standard, each plug is windproof and rainproof, and comes with a protective cover to keep dust and water out when not in use, and can withstand rain, snow, dust and other inclement weather.
      • Voice & Remote Control: Our outdoor smart plugs has voice & remote control function, compatible with Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, just need to give commands to the voice function, you can easily turn on/off the power, no need to go out and pick up your phone, you can make your smart home life more convenient and easy,no Hub Required.
      • Strong Wi-Fi Signal: Transmission distance up to 300 feet, the outdoor plug has a built-in power amplifier to provide you with a stable connection over longer distances, only supports 2.4GHz WIFI.
      • Easy Set Up and Use: Follow the included instructions to easily use the smart plugs that work with alexa. You can also set schedule and make it automatilly turn it on or off at the time you want, and the sunset/sunrise offset feature makes it even smarter and more convenient. Support 2.4GHz WIFI only.

      Strong Wi-Fi Signal

      Transmission distance up to 300 feet, the outdoor plug has a built-in power amplifier to provide you with a stable connection over longer distances.

      (Only supports 2.4GHz WIFI.)

      • Is it need a remote to control

        No, it does not require a remote.

      • Will it be suitable for outdoor use?

        Yes, GHome Smart Outdoor Smart Plug has an IP64 weather resistance rating, making it waterproof and resistant to rain, snow, and dust.

      • Is GHome Smart plug wifi connection stable and reliable?

        It has a strong Wi-Fi signal with transmission distance up to 300 feet and a built-in power amplifier for a stable connection over longer distances (Only support 2.4Ghz wifi).

      • What to do if you don't know how to use it?

        We provide 24-hour online support, we will answer questions to your queries.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2024

        We got this smart plug for our Christmas lights and it works great. We have several GHome switches in our house and have been pleased with them all. The app is very user friendly and intuitive.

        This switch was extremely simple to add to the app and get set up. Most of the time with these devices they need to update the firmware on the first use, and it automatically prompts you when setting it up and takes no time at all. I like that because it makes sure on your first use the product is going to be as up to date as possible.

        Both sides of the switch are independently programable via the app which makes it very handy for multiple items to get powew. You can choose to have the sockets activate at a set time. You can program it for different days of the week to do different things. It is extremely versatile and easy to use.

        We have it hooked up under a covered area so I can't speak to its weather proofing, but given their reputation I would believe whatever the listing says about it. It's time to upgrade your old light timer to something like this....you won't regret it!
